{"tid":1002120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舉報亂拋煙頭月賺2.5萬 網民：改行算了","createTime":"2019-01-30T16:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T17:14:55.000Z","uid":66271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"968df413f55423725229b0c224199cbeebb61f94","tid":1002120,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2260000/2263464/yan2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2260000%2F2263464%2Fyan2_600.jpg&h=534c36ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見人違規亂抛垃圾，有些人都盡公民責任挺身檢舉，然而在香港檢舉「垃圾蟲」只能靠正義感，機會成本較低，也就較少人會實際行動，但台灣就不同了。台灣為了保護環境，挺身檢舉亂抛煙頭等行爲也是有獎金的，所以台灣就出現了一群全職的「檢舉達人」，靠一個月檢舉數百宗個案竟月賺 10 萬台幣（約 HK$2.5 萬），比香港不少打工仔的月薪還要高！<br />\n<br />\n台灣環保局政策列明，一般亂丟煙頭會判罰台幣 1,200（約 HK$300）。民衆若成功檢舉，扣除稅金後則可以拎到台幣 480（約 HK$120）。所以，台灣一些檢舉達人就每天到處兜風，一見到有人邊騎車邊食煙、開車窗邊開車邊食煙等，就會偷偷跟上去，然後以車 Cam 等儀器拍下他們亂抛煙頭的證據。厲害的話，一個月就能檢舉 100 甚至 200 宗個案，相等於月入台幣 5 至 10 萬（約 HK$12,000 至 HK$24,000）。<br />\n<br />\n很多台灣網民都表示：「不亂丟不就沒事了」、「支持檢舉，不違規哪有獎金」、「可以來我家樓下抓嗎？」、「還有檢舉騎車、開車亂吐痰加丟垃圾也可領獎金」、「就是要有這種正義哥來拯救環境」、「環境是大家要一同保護的」然而不少網民的重點都落在獎金上，留言說：「以後手機要隨時開錄影了」、「檢舉撿起來，比 UBER 還好賺」、「賺外快啦」、「乾脆當主業算了，這樣賺應該比你做正業還快」、「應該可以月入十萬不是夢」就連香港網民也留言說香港應該推舉報獎金制。大家又覺得呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2263464/%E5%8F%B0%E7%94%B7%E6%AA%A2%E8%88%89%E4%BA%82%E6%8A%9B%E7%85%99%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E3%80%8D%E7%A0%B4%2010%20%E8%90%AC%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%AA%A2%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2263464%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%258A%259B%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25A0%25B4%252010%2520%25E8%2590%25AC%25EF%25BC%2581%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2588%25B6&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=195c5590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2263464/%E5%8F%B0%E7%94%B7%E6%AA%A2%E8%88%89%E4%BA%82%E6%8A%9B%E7%85%99%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA%E3%80%8D%E7%A0%B4%2010%20%E8%90%AC%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%87%89%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E6%AA%A2%E8%88%89%E5%88%B6</a>"},{"pid":"7a0199da023618c49e5a01c03e4d4a4b8e1d5d4c","tid":1002120,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc5bc7c6385f84e259af6382cb4fe8ba3c61718","tid":1002120,"uid":11598,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"抵啦&hellip;<br />\n如果香港有呢條例<br />\n落機鋪打個轉都賺成千銀都似"},{"pid":"65c5a68b26929021493b62a04480d5dac4cd387d","tid":1002120,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"72bb8759073eefb21b999c39359608e942844053","tid":1002120,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"一個火車頭賺120 咁我都去做啦"},{"pid":"0270670ce75338e756e47f0e03560b543077e3af","tid":1002120,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"直頭取消控煙辦D資源整呢個就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136a5ec507768b79e3ef885826c744a15075d178","tid":1002120,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:52:55.000Z","msg":"裝個車cam係旺角打個轉已經回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6154dd21bc84f76bc5415e85826f7d7ee3d1d6e5","tid":